Hello everyone,
Here is our robot release for 2022.

GitHub

GitHub - Oscats/SallyV_Oscats2022: This is the code for our 2022 Competition...

This is the code for our 2022 Competition FRC Robot - GitHub - Oscats/SallyV_Oscats2022: This is the code for our 2022 Competition FRC Robot

This was our first year using Java. We used Falcon motors run by CAN and did not use the Command Framework.

cad.onshape.com

Onshape

Sign in to Onshape, the #1 fastest growing CAD system in the world with over 2 million users.

On the design front, we used an Everybot-styled intake, and decided to use only one arm (which was a bit unstable). We lifted it with a gas shock which was incredibly simple and effective. We used two elevators, which were exciting. They work well. This was our first year with a successful climb, and we were able to do it often.

Thank you all for a wonderful season and all the help you gave us last year as well as all the years before.

Have fun and good luck this year.
